  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space is a vast black abyss. It must be illuminated! It seems like an absolutely impossible task. But somehow, Eric has to cope with it.<br>In this game, the Match-3 mechanics have been enhanced with improvements not found in our other games. Also, as usual, besides the Match-3 levels, there are bonus games and a city to build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game includes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 90 Match 3 levels and numerous bonus games: Solitaire, Mahjong, Spot the Difference, Jigsaw, as well as a city to build.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space is a vast black abyss. It must be illuminated! It seems like an absolutely impossible task. But somehow, Eric has to cope with it.<br>In this game, the Match-3 mechanics have been enhanced with improvements not found in our other games. Also, as usual, besides the Match-3 levels, there are bonus games and a city to build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game includes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 90 Match 3 levels and numerous bonus games: Solitaire, Mahjong, Spot the Difference, Jigsaw, as well as a city to build.</p>",
